Class Imaging

java.lang.Object
clinic.Appointment
clinic.Imaging
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Appointment>
public class Imaging extends Appointment
Represents an imaging appointment that extends the Appointment class. Includes additional details specific to imaging services, such as the type of imaging room. This class is used for appointments involving X-rays, ultrasounds, or CAT scans. Imaging services are assigned to a specific room based on the type of imaging service.

Dhawal Arora (Netid: da812)
